@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor Black
  LifeLineBorderColor Black
  LifeLineBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantBorderColor Black
  ParticipantBackgroundColor White
  ActorBorderColor Black
  ActorBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantFontColor Black
  ActorFontColor Black
}

actor "User" as User
participant "Frontend" as UI
participant "Backend API\nGET /api/wallets/by-email/:email" as API
participant "Database\nTable: Wallet" as DB
User->UI: Open wallet details page
UI->API: Request wallet details
API->DB: Retrieve wallet information
DB-->API: Return wallet data
API-->UI: Return wallet details
UI-->User: Display wallet balance and details

@enduml
